4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, and various data science tools, including Streamlit and Looker. The curriculum focuses on building predictive models and employing both supervised and unsupervised learning techniques.

Classes meet three times a week with a maximum of 12 students, ensuring personalized attention. The course culminates in a recognized certificate. Instructors have extensive industry experience, including expertise from top universities and institutions. The program is available in English and Spanish, catering to a diverse audience.

